<paragraph id="F71936E6FFFE4B5DFF1B0439FEDE7F14" blockId="7.[136,1452,266,1300]" pageId="7" pageNumber="174">Diagenesis: this species is characterized by its pure white appendiculate, curved and elongated cheilocystidia and bigger basidiospores.</paragraph>
