</taxonomicName>
, pure white color of pileus and medium sized basidiomata in diam. Compared with 
<taxonomicName id="30A64D65FFFE4B5DFCFC0198FC577AD0" box="[858,1022,1166,1192]" class="Agaricomycetes" family="Agaricaceae" genus="Micropsalliota" kingdom="Fungi" order="Agaricales" pageId="7" pageNumber="174" phylum="Basidiomycota" rank="species" species="subarginea">
